fields.title: God decides to destroy every living thing
Birth of Shem
fields.notes: Not all of Noah's sons listed in Gen 5:32 would have been born the same year. Shem was born when Noah was 102 in light of Gen 11:12.

Noah gets drunk and Canaan is cursed
Birth of Abraham
fields.notes: Not all of Terah's sons would have been born the same year. In light of Acts 7:4 and Genesis 12:4, Abraham was born when Terah was 130 years old.
